      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SIT AND STEER (7) wasn't far away at the finish when 5th and beaten only 4.5 lengths (24.54) at Bendigo. Form here at the trip sound including two wins. Better than the latest effort and deserves another chance. PROMOTE TILLY (2) hit the ground running and set it up early clocking 25.44 with a half a length win at Ballarat over 450m. Yet to taste defeat from two runs out of this box. Makes plenty of appeal if runs up to latest. PAW PHANTOM (4) turned spotting a big start finishing seventh (26.35) last time in a Grade 5 at Geelong. Has ability and can measure up. RATTLER (8) was out of the money at this circuit last start but can atone.",
